  "detailed_description": "<h1>RECOMMENDED FOR YOU</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong>Primal Survivos </strong> it's an insane top down shooter with unique weird creatures from this underground primal world.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492150/extras/4660056dbe050cae74b00a978e6d12ee.poster.avif?t=1688073139\" width=602 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492150/extras/4660056dbe050cae74b00a978e6d12ee.webm?t=1688073139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492150/extras/4660056dbe050cae74b00a978e6d12ee.mp4?t=1688073139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features</strong><br>◘ 50 Skills sets represented with unique card design for a unique experience every run!<br>◘ 25 Permanent upgrades<br>◘ 12 Classes<br>◘ 12 Weapons<br>◘ 3 Bosses with unique behaviors <br>◘ 10 Minutes Bonfire gameplay mode for busy gamers<br>◘ 2 Game Modes with unique classes and weapons<br><br><br><strong>Use Cards to Upgrade Your Skills</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492150/extras/a34859dd88fb641d70476c3691fa37fb.poster.avif?t=1688073139\" width=602 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492150/extras/a34859dd88fb641d70476c3691fa37fb.webm?t=1688073139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492150/extras/a34859dd88fb641d70476c3691fa37fb.mp4?t=1688073139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Improve your Skills and Make some DAMAGE!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loo